      <p class="mt-2 text-stone-700">To the maximum extent permitted by law, Family Hubble is not liable for indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or for lost profits or revenues.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="py-8 border-t border-stone-200/70">
